{"_id":"XpLQs2UdResBYlk1","name":"Low Profile","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"Even though you have had your name in the spotlight, you have managed to downplay your involvement in events. When a roll is made to recognize you, the roll is at -4. This modifier can be doubled by spending a Benny.</p><p><b>Source: </b>Pulp Fantastic, page 80","notes":"Pulp Fantastic, page 80","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"N"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"GJDx6zyRouhhfhRq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_1zofuj1e709","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"YFLc37aGkpKhnWy8","name":"Targeteer","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"The Pilot knows how to bring the vessel itself to bear during a dogfight, and as such adds Handling to Shooting Trait rolls with onboard weapons.</p><p><b>Source: </b>Pilot Edges for Savage Worlds, page ","notes":"Pilot Edges for Savage Worlds, page ","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Piloting d6, Shooting d6, Electronics d6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"GJDx6zyRouhhfhRq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_us2p9cunc3","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"ZsmOLiIPYMKmY1Qz","name":"Exceptional Individual","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"Masked Crusaders are exotic individuals with a wide range of abilities akin to the pulp heroes of later generations.<p>This Edge grants a Masked Crusader any Combat Edge, regardless of Rank Requirements.All other Requirements must be met as usual. It may only be taken once (usually during character creation).</p><p><b>Source: </b>Rippers Resurrected, page 16","notes":"Rippers Resurrected, page 16","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"N, Faction (Masked Crusaders)"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"GJDx6zyRouhhfhRq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_dygc9en5q1d","color":"#000000"}}}
